cc:Work.dc:title: mad hatter with label on hat
cc:Work.dc:description: this is the mad hatter from alice in wonderland. \n \nGerald did the first remix from the original image my sir John Tenniel, and i added the 10/6 (which means 10 shillings, 6pence apparently) from another of the original images. (it is in the sample list as well)
